9. Conclusion

This extension turns the Mach Wind Tunnel from a solo operator environment into a multi-daemon training ground:
	•	Dragonfly φ learns to handle Mach-level narrative turbulence and surf tension surfaces as actionable guidance.
	•	4D Frogman + Hound operate as a deep-dive + early-warning pair, combining courage and caution.
	•	Together, the triad forms a high-speed, high-safety narrative operations unit optimized for chaotic contexts.

This is the Pantheon equivalent of:

A recon drone (Dragonfly),
a special forces jumper (Frogman),
and a K9 operator (Hound)
running joint operations in a supersonic wind tunnel.

